2007;;Spiral;;American;;Joel David Moore, Adam Green;;Amber Tamblyn, Joel David Moore, Zachary Levi;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spiral_(2007_film);;The story follows lonely introvert Mason, a telesales insurance company worker by day and talented painter as well as a lover of classic jazz by night. His only friend is his boss, Berkeley (Levi), who keeps an eye on him and humors his bizarre behavior. When awkward Mason meets social Amber, a new co-worker, he begins to come out of himself, and reveals the depth and darkness of his mind.